org.fujion.common

Class Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fujion.common.Logger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.commons.logging.Log, ILogger

    public class Logger
extends Object
implements ILogger
    Provides a wrapper for Commons logger to allow use of lambda expressions.
